codex-lmstudio-kotlin
=====================

A Kotlin Multiplatform port of the `codex-rs/lmstudio/` crate from the
openai/codex repository — the LM Studio OSS provider client used by
`codex-cli`.

The upstream `codex-rs` is dual-licensed Apache-2.0 OR MIT, copyright
OpenAI and the codex contributors. The Kotlin translation here is a
derivative work, distributed under the same dual Apache-2.0 OR MIT
terms. All algorithmic and structural design credit — the
LM-Studio-server reachability check, the `lms`-CLI `find_lms` lookup
strategy, the `download_model` / `load_model` flows, the test layout
using sandbox-network-disabled env-gated mocks — belongs to the
upstream contributors.

Vendored Rust source is fetched into `tmp/codex-lmstudio/` by
`tools/fetch-rust-source.sh` and is not tracked in this repo
(see `.gitignore`). The Kotlin port lives at
`src/commonMain/kotlin/io/github/kotlinmania/codex/lmstudio/`. Each
ported `.kt` file carries a `// port-lint:` header pointing at the
specific Rust source path it was translated from.

Upstream:
