  License:    LICENSE-APACHE OR LICENSE-MIT (your choice; matches upstream)

Translation rules — see CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md. The short version:
line-by-line transliteration; `reqwest::Client` is replaced by
`io.ktor.client.HttpClient`; `tokio::test` becomes
`kotlinx-coroutines-test`'s `runTest`; `serde_json::Value` becomes
`kotlinx.serialization.json.JsonElement`; `std::process::Command` for
the `lms get` invocation becomes a platform-native suspend wrapper.
